<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<XCSS version="1.0"><![CDATA[/*
* 아이콘 규칙
   icon 에 패딩을 주는 경우 클리핑 처리 방식이 넥사브라우저와 웹브라우저가 다름
   icon 은 스트레치 처리되지 않음
   icon 크기를 폰트+페딩 에 맞게 조정필요
* 하위컨트롤 이벤트 전파 ( selected 등이 전달되지 않음 )
* 프로그래스바에 라운드보더 제거 ( 매뉴얼 제약도 명시 필요 )
* Tabbutton 버튼하단 none border 처리를 직접해야함
* tabpage / Div / PopupDiv 등에 Form 과 다른 배경색을 주고자 하는 경우 Form 배경색은 투명하게 처리해야함
* cellexpandbutton 배경을 투명으로 주는 경우 셀 텍스트위에 겹쳐져서 표시되므로, 버튼 형태의 배경색 지정 필요
* 콤보리스트 등 팝업 처리되는 컨트롤에 컬러 및 폰트 지정 필요
* 아래 컨트롤들의 정렬 기능만 별도로 지정하고 나머지는 기본값으로 처리
   * popupmenuitemhotkeytext : -nexa-text-align : right;
   * progressbartext :  : -nexa-text-align : center;
   * imagetext : -nexa-text-align : center;
   * .Grid .head .row .cell : -nexa-text-align : center;
   * .Grid .summary .row .cell : -nexa-text-align : center;
   * .StatusBarControl .resizegrip : -nexa-vertical-align : bottom;
   * .Spin .spinedit : -nexa-text-align : right;

정식출시전까지 아래 변경이력 주석으로 관리함
20160831
   1. Form추가 [RP68483]
   2. Grid .checkbox추가 [RP68497]
   3. DatePicker수정 [RP없음]
   4. menu/popupmenu .spinUp/Down Button 추가 [RP69135]
20160913
  1. Flash Player삭제 [RP69386]
  2. next/prev button으로 명칭 변경 [RP69450,68873]
  3. Grid .head .button추가 [RP69335]
20160930
   1. Tab next/prev Button CSS 및 이미지명 수정 - RP69490
   2. Menu next/prev Button CSS 및 이미지명 수정 - RP69490
   3. PopUP Menu next/prev Button CSS 및 이미지명 수정 - RP69490
   4. Div의 -nexa-text-align 삭제 -RP69539
   5. Grid .cell .expandbutton추가 -RP68632
20161006
   1. border => -nexa-border 명칭 변경 [RP68646]
20161012
   1. Edit계열 nexa-padding 10px => 3px로 변경
   2. Edit계열 background컬러 추가 - RP69777
20161208
   1. popupmenuitemicon Style 설정 제거
20161222
   1. Menu / PopupMenu  navigationbutton  이미지 표시 오류 : RP71095
20170125
   1. nexatreeline 부분 제거 : 변경 가능한 컨트롤이 아니라 고정 값을 가지는 컨트롤임 [RP71432]
20170302
   1. fileuploaditemedit nexa-text-align의 left 로 변경[RP71925]
20170315
   1. Plugin, WebBrowser, PluginControl, WebBrowserControl의 속성 -nexa-border만 남기고 삭제함 [RP71782]
20170403
   1. .Grid .body .row .cell .celltreeline의 속성 -nexa-border 추가함 [RP72421]
20170412
   1. Calendar 하위 컨트롤 명칭 변경
   - spinupbutton -> calendarspinupbutton
   - spindownbutton -> calendarspindownbutton [RP72490]
20170508
   1. default value 추가 [RP73121]
20170517
   1. cellexpandbutton 	background 변경 [RP73331]
20170526
   1. default properties 추가 지정 작업
20170712
   1. FileDownload 컴포넌트 pushed userstatus  추가 [RP74090]
20170804
   1. windows 작업표시줄에 생기는 icon [RP74438]
     - -nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/titlebar_icon_nexacro17.ico');

*/


/**********************Frame/Form***********************************************/
.Form
{
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	color : #333333;
	background : #ffffff;
	-nexa-border : 0px none;
}

.Form[userstatus=contents]
{
	background : transparent;
}

.Form[status=disabled]
{
	color : #999999; 
}


.MainFrame,.ChildFrame,.FrameSet,.VFrameSet,.HFrameSet,.TileFrameSet
{
	/*별도스타일없음*/
}

.MainFrame .titlebar .titleicon
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/titlebar_icon_nexacro17.ico');
}

/**********************Button***********************************************/
.Button
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #7099f8;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 20px;
	background : #ffffff;
	color : #2c59c4;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	cursor : pointer;
	border-radius : 3px;
}
.Button[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-text-decoration : underline;
	background :#edf4fd;
	color : #2c59c4;
}
.Button[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1;
	color : #2c59c4;
}
.Button[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #e5e5e5;
	color : #999999;
	cursor : default;
}
/**********************FileDownload***********************************************/
/**********************FileUpload***********************************************/
/***** FileDownload *****/
.FileDownload
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 10px 0px 10px;
	background : #e6e6e6;
	cursor : pointer;
}
.FileDownload[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4a83d1;
}
.FileDownload[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #c6c6c6;
	background : #f2f2f2;
	color : #888888;
	cursor : default;
}
/***** FileUpload *****/
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditemedit,
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditemedit[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #bbbbbb;
	background : #ffffff;
}
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditemedit[status=disabled]
{
	background : #e8e8e8;
}
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditembutton
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 4px 10px 4px 10px;
	background : #e6e6e6;
	cursor : pointer;
}
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditembutton[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4a83d1;
}
.FileUpload .fileuploaditem .fileuploaditembutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #c6c6c6;
	background : #f2f2f2;
	color : #888888;
	cursor : default;
}

.ButtonControl
{
	background : transparent;
	-nexa-border : 0px none;
}


/**********************Calendar***********************************************/
.Calendar
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 1px;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";

}
.Calendar[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4272e1;
}
.Calendar[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px;
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1; 
} 
.Calendar[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #efefef;
}
.Calendar[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	color : #999999;
	background : #efefef;
}


.Calendar .calendaredit
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px 10px 1px 15px;
}

.Calendar .dropbutton
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Calendar.png');
}

.Calendar .dropbutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Calendar_D.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspinupbutton
{
	-nexa-padding : 2px 0px 0px 0px;
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspinupbutton[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_O.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspinupbutton[userstatus=pushed]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_P.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspinupbutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_D.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspindownbutton
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px 0px 3px 0px;
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spindown.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspindownbutton[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spindown_O.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspindownbutton[userstatus=pushed]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spindown_P.png');
}

.Calendar .calendarspindownbutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spindown_D.png');
}


/**********************CheckBox***********************************************/
.CheckBox
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box.png");
	-nexa-border : 2px solid transparent;
	-nexa-text-padding :  1px 10px;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
}
.CheckBox[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_O.png");
}
.CheckBox[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box.png");
	-nexa-text-decoration : none;
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1;
}
.CheckBox[userstatus=selected]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_OS.png");
	-nexa-text-decoration : underline;
}
.CheckBox[userstatus=selected][status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_OS.png");
	-nexa-text-decoration : underline;
}
.CheckBox[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_D.png");
	color : #999999;
}
.CheckBox[status=disabled][userstatus=selected]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_DS.png");
	color : #999999;
}

/**********************Combo***********************************************/
.Combo
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 3px 1px 15px;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";

}
.Combo[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4272e1;
}
.Combo[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 3px 1px 14px;
}
.Combo[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #e5e5e5;
	color : #999999;
}
.Combo[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #e5e5e5;
}
.Combo .comboedit
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px;
}
.Combo .dropbutton
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/cmb_WF_Drop.png");
	cursor : pointer;
}
.Combo .dropbutton[status=mouseover],.Combo .dropbutton[userstatus=pushed]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/cmb_WF_Drop_O.png");
}
.Combo .dropbutton[status=disabled]
{
	opacity : 0.50;
}
.Combo .combolist
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
}
.Combo .combolist .listboxitem
{
	-nexa-padding : 6px 10px;
}
.Combo .combolist .listboxitem[status=mouseover]
{
	background : #e7e7e7;
}
.Combo .combolist .listboxitem[userstatus=selected]
{
	background : #cee9fd;
	color : #333333;
}
/**********************Edit***********************************************/
.Edit
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 15px 1px 15px;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
}
.Edit[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4272e1;
}
.Edit[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 15px 1px 14px;
}
.Edit[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #efefef;
}
.Edit[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	color : #999999;
	background : #efefef;
}
.Edit[userstatus=nulltext]
{
	color : #666666;
}
/**********************Grid***********************************************/
.Grid
{
	background : #ffffff;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #125dae, 1px solid #b7b1b2, 1px solid #b7b1b2, 1px solid #b7b1b2;
}
/*-----------------------------------head------------------------------------*/
.Grid .head .row .cell
{
	font : 17px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	color : #333333;
	background : #f5f5f5;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #cacaca;
	-nexa-padding : 4px 4px 4px 4px;
	-nexa-text-align : center;
}
.Grid .head .row .cell[status=focused]
{
	font : 17px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	color : #333333;
	background : #f5f5f5;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #cacaca;
	-nexa-padding : 4px 4px 4px 4px;
	-nexa-text-align : center;
	-nexa-text-decoration : underline;
}

.Grid .body .row .cell.Cell_WF_Fixed
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #cacaca, 1px solid #cacaca, 2px solid black, 1px solid #cacaca;
}
.Grid .body .row .cell
{
	color : #333333;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #d2d2d2;
	-nexa-padding : 4px 15px;
}

.Grid .body .row .cell[status=mouseover]
{
	background : #f6f6f6;
}

.Grid .body .row .cell[userstatus=selected]
{
	background : #f2f9ff;
}

.Grid .body .row .cell[status=disabled]
{
	color : #999999;
}

/*-----------------------------------bodycellbutton:ButtonControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellcalendar:CalendarControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellcheckbox:CheckBoxControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellcombo:ComboControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycelledit:EditControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellexpandbutton------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellimage:별도스타일없음------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellmaskedit:MaskEditControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycellprogressbar:ProgressBarControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycelltextarea:TextAreaControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------bodycelltreeitem:------------------------------------*/

/*-----------------------------------summary------------------------------------*/
.Grid .summary
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #c8c1c2, 0px none, 0px none, 0px none;
}

.Grid .summary .row .cell
{
	font : bold 13px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	color : #333333;
	background : #fdfbe5;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #c8c1c2;
	-nexa-text-align : center;
}
/*-----------------------------------summarycellbutton:ButtonControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellcalendar:CalendarControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellcheckbox:CheckBoxControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellcombo:ComboControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycelledit:EditControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellexpandbutton------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellimage:별도스타일없음------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellmaskedit:MaskEditControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycellprogressbar:ProgressBarControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycelltextarea:TextAreaControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
/*-----------------------------------summarycelltreeitem:------------------------------------*/

/*-----------------------------------Grid hscrollbar:------------------------------------*/
.Grid .hscrollbar
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b1b1b1, 0px none, 0px none, 0px none;
}
/*-----------------------------------Grid vscrollbar:------------------------------------*/
.Grid .vscrollbar
{
	-nexa-border : 0px none, 0px none, 0px none, 1px solid #b1b1b1;
}


/**********************GridCellControl***********************************************/
/*-----------------------------------cellbutton:ButtonControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
.GridCellControl .cellbutton
{
	font : 15px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
	color : #555555;
	background : linear-gradient(to top,#eaeaea,#ffffff);
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #c2c2c2;
}

.GridCellControl .cellbutton[status=mouseover],.GridCellControl .cellbutton[status=focused]
{
	background : linear-gradient(to top,#e7e7e7,#fefefe);
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a0a0a0;
}

.GridCellControl .cellbutton[userstatus=pushed],.GridCellControl .cellbutton[userstatus=selected]
{
	background : linear-gradient(to top,#fefefe,#e9e9e9);
}

.GridCellControl .cellbutton[status=disabled]
{
	color : #bbbbbb;
	background : #f5f5f5;
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #d9d9d9; 
}

/*-----------------------------------cellcalendar:CalendarControl과 동일------------------------------------*/ 
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px ;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";

}
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4272e1;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1; 
} 
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #efefef;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	color : #999999;
	background : #efefef;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .calendaredit
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px 10px 1px 15px;
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .dropbutton
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Calendar.png');
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .dropbutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Calendar_D.png');
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .calendarspinupbutton
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup.png');
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .calendarspinupbutton[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_O.png');
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .calendarspinupbutton[userstatus=pushed]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_P.png');
}

.GridCellControl .cellcalendar .calendarspinupbutton[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL('theme://images/btn_WF_Spinup_D.png');
}

/*-----------------------------------cellcheckbox:CheckBoxControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box.png");
	-nexa-text-padding :  0px 10px 0px 10px; 
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_O.png");
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box.png"); 
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[userstatus=selected]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_OS.png"); 
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[userstatus=selected][status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_OS.png"); 
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_D.png"); 
}
.GridCellControl .cellcheckbox[status=disabled][userstatus=selected] 
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/chk_WF_Box_DS.png");
}


/*-----------------------------------cellcombo:ComboControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
.GridCellControl .cellcombo
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 3px 1px 15px;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";

}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo[status=mouseover]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #4272e1;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo[status=focused]
{
	-nexa-border : 2px solid #4272e1;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 3px 1px 14px;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo[status=disabled]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #e5e5e5;
	color : #999999;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo[status=readonly]
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #a6a6a6;
	background : #e5e5e5;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .comboedit
{
	-nexa-padding : 0px;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .dropbutton
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/cmb_WF_Drop.png");
	cursor : pointer;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .dropbutton[status=mouseover],.GridCellControl .cellcombo .dropbutton[userstatus=pushed]
{
	-nexa-icon : URL("theme://images/cmb_WF_Drop_O.png");
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .dropbutton[status=disabled]
{
	opacity : 0.50;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .combolist
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .combolist .listboxitem
{
	-nexa-padding : 8px 10px 8px 10px;
}.GridCellControl .cellcombo .combolist .listboxitem[status=mouseover]
{
	background : #e7e7e7;
}
.GridCellControl .cellcombo .combolist .listboxitem[userstatus=selected]
{
	background : #cee9fd;
	color : #333333;
}

/*-----------------------------------celledit:EditControl과 동일------------------------------------*/
.GridCellControl .celledit
{
	-nexa-border : 1px solid #b2b2b2;
	-nexa-padding : 0px 15px 1px 15px;
	background : #fbfbfb;
	color : #333333;
	font : 16px "NotoSansKR-Regular";
}
.GridCellControl .celledit[status=mouseover]
{
